<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "S8T40A3126002" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Rear Drive Shaft Assembly Removal and Installation
</title>
<servinfosub id = "S8T40A3126002001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Undo caulking (1) of drive shaft nut (2) and then remove drive shaft nut.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5JB0A311003.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.523mm" ver = "01" gw = "176" gh = "109"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hoist vehicle and remove wheel.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drain rear differential oil.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove rear drive shaft as follows.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Left side drive shaft assembly 
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Support lower arm (1) with jack (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8T401230007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.039mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "122"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove left side rear wheel speed sensor. 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ESP&#174; model: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4606006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ABS model: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4506008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove left side control rod outer bolt, trailing rod rear bolt and lower arm outer bolt. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A2306028"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Using tire lever (1), pull out left side drive shaft joint (2) while turning left side drive shaft joint in parallel with rear differential gear case so as to release snap ring fitting of joint spline at differential side.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9T401312002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.797mm" ver = "01" gw = "172" gh = "161"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove left side drive shaft assembly.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Right side drive shaft assembly 
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Remove rear drive shaft flange nuts (1), and then remove right side drive shaft assembly (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9T401312003.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.570mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "115"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.166in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Drive shaft flange
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "S8T40A3126002002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
Install drive shaft assembly by reversing removal procedure and noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Protect oil seals and boots from any damage, preventing them from unnecessary contact while installing drive shaft.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not hit joint boot with hammer.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Inserting joint only by hands is allowed.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten rear drive shaft nuts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A3126001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten left side lower arm outer bolt, trailing rod rear bolt and control rod outer bolt to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A2306028"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten rear wheel speed sensor bolt to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4506008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Fill rear differential with oil as specified. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A3226001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
